---
title: Creamy Bacon and Mushroom Pie with Chives and Garlicky Green Beans
description: This Creamy Bacon and Mushroom Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-bacon-and-mushroom-pie-465703eb.jpg
